ivardefs.name: fivePrime

ivardefs.name: length
ivardefs.desc: The length of the sequence shall be captured.

ivardefs.name: linkage_
ivardefs.desc: The linkages between sugar residues will also be captured.

ivardefs.name: sequence
ivardefs.desc: Actual nucleotide sequence notation from 5' to 3' end using standard single letter codes. In addition to the base sequence, sugar and type of phosphate or non-phosphate linkage should also be captured.

ivardefs.name: subunit
ivardefs.desc: Index of linear sequences of nucleic acids in order of decreasing length. Sequences of the same length will be ordered by molecular weight. Subunits that have identical sequences will be repeated and have sequential subscripts.

ivardefs.name: threePrime

properties.desc: Subunits are listed in order of decreasing length; sequences of the same length will be ordered by molecular weight; subunits that have identical sequences will be repeated multiple times.
